Email Templates Library
High-Performing Cold Email Frameworks for AI Agents
Purpose: Reference library of proven email templates with examples, best practices, and ICP guidance.

Usage: AI agents should select templates based on:

Prospect context (signals, triggers, pain points)
ICP match
Outreach objective
Engagement stage


